        {
            "name": "Giant Tick",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "This grotesque tick is the size of a dog and scurries with surprising speed.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 15",
